      "comment": "ZIPPING DALY (3) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, paving the way for a 1.5 lengths win at The Gardens over 400m in 22.97. Well placed and can measure up. DESPICABLE MILO (4) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when third (17.83) at Richmond Straight in a Grade 5. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. NOT CLIFFORD (2) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 6 lengths into third (22.91) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can feature again. BUTTER'S BETTER (1) boasts a solid strike-rate from this box.",
